responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "04E1C1EE4E8C6C169241949B2B34B854", "There is no mercy within this forsaken land. As if goblins were not enough, the seeds of of my demise have sprouted upon my family\'s estate. It\'s as if a curse has overtaken my name. For Sevens Sake!")
